<P>The facts related in the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="4 letters">ription, &s;ufficiently prove that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">e <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> a man of great natural parts, and tho&s;e <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> improved, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter">or the worthy perform|ance <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 span"> h s high &s;tation in the Church <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word">.</P>
