<ITEM>After who&s;e death, the &s;aid Lord Archbi&s;hop appointed Ja&s;per Yardley, Gent. to &s;ucceed him. He died May 31&s;t, 1639&mdash;Ma&s;ter, 9 years, 2 months, 1 day.</ITEM>
